org.apache.storm.transactional

インタフェース ICommitter

  • 既知の実装クラスのリスト:
    CountingCommitBolt, KeyedCountingCommitterBolt, TransactionalGlobalCount.UpdateGlobalCount, TransactionalWords.KeyedCountUpdater

    public interface ICommitter

    This marks an IBatchBolt within a transactional topology as a committer. This causes the finishBatch method to be called in order of the transactions.
